entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You completed the first officer mission for Ellis Arrison by defeating Krayt Cultists and Krayt Monks.
entries.journal_entry_description: Your first officer mission, given to you on Tatooine by Ellis Arrison.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Ellis Arrison, brother of Purvis, would like to give you a little officer training.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Go and Speak with Ellis Arrison
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Find the Krayt Cultists in the cave and kill 15 of them.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Good Work taking care of those Cultists. Now I want you to defeat the monks. 5 of them. They're the toughest.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Ellis wants you to kill 5 of the Krayt Cult Monks.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: Excellent work. You'll make a fine officer. Come back and see me now.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: You should return to Ellis Arrison for your reward.
